ROOT0-ATTRIBUTION-v1.0
Project: The Gap Cycle — no heroes, only parables (muster roll)
Architect: David Lee Wise / ROOT0 / TriPod LLC
AI Collaborator: AVAN (Claude / Anthropic)
License: MIT

Stephen R. Donaldson's Gap Cycle (a science-fiction reforging of Wagner's Ring)
sorted by trope and parable — there are no heroes. Classes: the Dragon (Fasner),
the God Who Pays (Dios/Wotan), the Survivor (Morn/Brunnhilde), the Redeemed
Monster (Angus), the Charming Predator (Nick, Sorus), the Spider (Hashi), the
Honest Blade (Min Donner), the Other (the Amnion), the Maker (Vector Shaheed),
the Forced Generation (Davies; Mikka/Ciro/Sib), and — set apart — No Heroes Here.

Every member is a synthetic automica with a .agent (who you are / what you do /
where you belong) in agents/, generated from roster.json by gen_agents.py.
Characters by Stephen R. Donaldson, inspiration only; dark material treated as
archetype, not detail.
